CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1957, pg. A17 reads: " "King And Queen"... for 1957 are there delightful young people. Miss Alice Jean Weatherly is the "queen" and William Hampton is the "king."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of "Queen" Alice Jean Weatherly and "King" William Hampton, posed at base of staircase in Penn Sheraton Hotel for the Alpha Kappa Alpha 1957 Cotillion
